lead_paragraph: The Monitore Toscano of the 5th, contains a Ministerial dispatch, addressed to the Prefect of Florence, recommending him not to allow The Constituzionale to publish lists of candidates for municipal counsellorships, such publications being considered an infringement of the rights of electors.
